System Requirements:

Linux, Windows 7 or up, Mac OSX
Widescreen display with a resolution of 1920x1080 recommended
150 MB Free RAM
75 MB Free graphics memory
Audio output (Speaker or Headphones)
Mouse
Keyboard

To run the game you need Panda3D 1.10
which can be downloaded at:
http://www.panda3d.org/download.php?sdk&version=devel
